last_episode_to_air.overview: Deewangi is a 2019 Pakistani romantic drama television series, produced by Abdullah Kadwani and Asad Qureshi under 7th Sky Entertainment. It started airing on Geo Entertainment from 18 December 2019. It has Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in leads.
